<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Belam chingte'n belam ching a,
 Zana a chut lai un;
 Lalpa Angel a hung kum a,
 A vel uh a salh vak.

[V2]
 2. Lau leh linga a um lai un,
 &quot;Lau kiu!&quot; ti'n a lungmuon;
 &quot;Chanchin Pha kipahum mahmah,
 Mitin di'n Ka hun puo'i.&quot;

[V3]
 3. &quot;Tuni'n David khuo ah nang di'n,
 David phunglai achun;
 Hukdampa, Lal Krista A pieng,
 Ziehi a tiemtehna.&quot;

[V4]
 4. &quot;Ziechun van Nausen va mu'n lau,
 Mihiem muhtheih a um;
 Tawmtaka puon a kituom in,
 Gan ankuong a kuol in.&quot;

[V5]
 5. Seraph-in ziechuh a gen a,
 Van Angel mithiengte;
 Pathien pak in a hung lang ui,
 A kipah lau chuh sa'n.

[V6]
 6. &quot;Chung Pathien chuh lopi hen la!
 Lei ah chamna leng hen!
 Hai talodi'n kideihsakna,
 Van leh lei mi'n nei hen!&quot;</lyrics>
<title>WHILE SHEPHERD WATCHED</title>
<hymn_number>51</hymn_number>
</song>